---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Cosmetic Dentistry" 
  category="Smile Enhancement"
  description="Transform your smile with our advanced cosmetic treatments. From whitening to complete smile makeovers."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1606811971618-4486d14f3f99?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Your Dream Smile Awaits</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Modern cosmetic dentistry combines art and science to create beautiful, natural-looking smiles. 
        Whether you want a subtle enhancement or a complete transformation, we have the solution for you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Popular Cosmetic Treatments
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Zoom Whitening -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-accent-200/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Zoom! Teeth Whitening</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Professional whitening that brightens teeth up to 8 shades in just one hour.</p>
          <a href="/services/zoom-whitening" class="text-primary-900 font-medium hover:text-primary-800">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Invisalign -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Invisalign® Clear Aligners</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Straighten your teeth discreetly without traditional metal braces.</p>
          <a href="/services/invisalign" class="text-primary-900 font-medium hover:text-primary-800">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Veneers -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-accent-200/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Porcelain Veneers</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Custom-made shells that perfect your smile's shape, size, and color.</p>
          <a href="/services/veneers" class="text-primary-900 font-medium hover:text-primary-800">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Dental Bonding -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200/30 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-20 h-20 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Dental Bonding</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Quick, affordable fix for chips, gaps, and minor imperfections.</p>
          <a href="/services/bonding" class="text-primary-900 font-medium hover:text-primary-800">Learn more →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Complete Smile Makeovers
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
        A smile makeover combines multiple cosmetic treatments to achieve your ideal smile. 
        During your consultation, we'll design a personalized treatment plan that may include:
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <span>Teeth whitening for a brighter foundation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <span>Orthodontics to perfect alignment</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary-900 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <span>Veneers or bonding for shape and size</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">4</span>
            </div>
            <span>Gum contouring for ideal proportions</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">5</span>
            </div>
            <span>Crown replacement for consistency</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <span class="text-primary-900 text-xs font-bold">6</span>
            </div>
            <span>Final polish and perfection</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">
          The Consultation Process
        </h3>
        <ol class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary-900">1.</span>
            <span>Discuss your smile goals and concerns</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary-900">2.</span>
            <span>Complete examination and digital imaging</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary-900">3.</span>
            <span>Review treatment options and timeline</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary-900">4.</span>
            <span>Create your personalized treatment plan</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="font-bold text-primary-900">5.</span>
            <span>Discuss investment and payment options</span>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-4">
          Why Choose Us?
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Advanced training in cosmetic dentistry</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>State-of-the-art technology and materials</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Hundreds of smile transformations</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-300 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Flexible payment and financing options</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Free Cosmetic Consultation
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Discover your smile's potential with a complimentary cosmetic consultation. We'll discuss 
        your goals, explore treatment options, and create a customized plan just for you.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Consultation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/zoom-whitening" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Zoom! Whitening</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Brighten your smile in one hour</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/invisalign" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Invisalign®</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Clear alternative to braces</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/veneers" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Porcelain Veneers</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Perfect your smile</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How much does cosmetic dentistry cost?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Costs vary widely depending on the treatments you choose. Simple procedures like whitening 
        start around $500, while comprehensive smile makeovers can range from $5,000 to $30,000. 
        We offer flexible payment plans and will provide a detailed quote during your consultation.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How long do cosmetic treatments last?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        With proper care: Teeth whitening lasts 1-3 years, bonding 3-10 years, veneers 10-15 years, 
        and crowns 10-20 years. Regular dental care and good oral hygiene help maximize longevity.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Will my insurance cover cosmetic dentistry?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most cosmetic procedures are not covered by insurance. However, treatments that also restore 
        function (like crowns or some bonding) may have partial coverage. We'll help you understand 
        your benefits and maximize any available coverage.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>